  "summary": "Main\nBy Jeffrey Landsberg\nAs we discussed for clients earlier last month, China's coal imports in November totaled a record 55 million tons. Import data by source is now available and shows that imports from Indonesia totaled 25.6 million tons. This has marked the largest volume seen since December 2020.",
